\fs28 \cf2 Transition:  Today I want to talk about a Character that tends to be forgotten and yet I believe is central to the success of this story on many levels.\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\fs36 \cf0 GOD
\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}We talk about Mary all the time, but compared to Joseph she didn\'92t do much.  She was just told that she was pregnant and went with it\'85it was passive.  \
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Joseph was told what to do multiple times and acted upon it\'85it was active.  How many times did he have to change jobs, friends, house, relationships, because of a dream that God had given him.  \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 19\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub Because Joseph her husband was faithful to the law, and yet
\fs15 \super [e]
\fs24 \nosupersub did not want to expose her to public disgrace, he had in mind to divorce\'a0her quietly.\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 20\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But after he had considered this, an angel\'a0of the Lord appeared to him in a dream\'a0and said, \'93Joseph son of David, do not be afraid to take Mary home as your wife, because what is conceived in her is from the Holy Spirit.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 21\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub She will give birth to a son, and you are to give him the name Jesus,
\fs15 \super [f]
\fs24 \nosupersub \'a0because he will save his people from their sins.\'94\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 24\'a0
\f3\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When Joseph woke up, he did what the angel\'a0of the Lord had commanded him and took Mary home as his wife.  Matthew 1\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0\cf4 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some commentary\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf4 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 13\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub When they had gone, an angel\'a0of the Lord appeared to Joseph in a dream.\'a0\'93Get up,\'94 he said, \'93take the child and his mother and escape to Egypt. Stay there until I tell you, for Herod is going to search for the child to kill him.\'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 14\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So he got up, took the child and his mother during the night and left for Egypt,\'a0Matthew 2\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0\cf3 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa150\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0

\f2\b\fs18 \cf3 \super 19\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub After Herod died, an angel\'a0of the Lord appeared in a dream\'a0to Joseph in Egypt\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 20\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and said, \'93Get up, take the child and his mother and go to the land of Israel, for those who were trying to take the child\'92s life are dead.\'94\

\f2\b\fs18 \super 21\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub So he got up, took the child and his mother and went to the land of Israel.\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 22\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub But when he heard that Archelaus was reigning in Judea in place of his father Herod, he was afraid to go there. Having been warned in a dream,\'a0he withdrew to the district of Galilee,\'a0
\f2\b\fs18 \super 23\'a0
\f1\b0\fs24 \nosupersub and he went and lived in a town called Nazareth.\'a0So was fulfilled\'a0what was said through the prophets, that he would be called a Nazarene.  Matthew 2\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qc\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}4 times Joseph changed the direction of his life because of what God was leading him to\'85because of the dreams that he was having.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf2 Transition:  What do you dream about?\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Not necessarily the dreams you dream at night\'85but the things you day dream about?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The things that maybe God has put in your heart to accomplish or fix or do.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 YOU
\f1\b0\fs24 \uc0\u8232 \u8232 
\f0\b\fs28 3 keys to following God:\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Be careful/open\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}While Joseph I\'92m sure was looking to follow God I\'92m positive this wasn\'92t what he was thinking.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}But He was open to what God wanted him to do and not what he wanted to do.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Are you willing to lose everything to follow God?\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Joseph lost everything!\
\pard\tx2380\tx2880\pardeftab720\li2880\fi-2880\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl3\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His job\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His extended family\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His friends\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His financial security\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His house\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}His land\
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}In one moment Joseph lost it all!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}And he didn\'92t pause and ask is it really worth it\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Be clear\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1\cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Clarity gives you confidence \
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}This is so important because your confidence will take a hit.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Can you imagine how Joseph had to feel at family reunions and such\'85with people questioning how stupid and foolish he was to believe his wayward wife?\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}The moment you start to let others know about your dream Satan will use others to attack and many times it is the people who are closest to you.  \
\pard\tx1660\tx2160\pardeftab720\li2160\fi-2160\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl2\cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Many times they will do this because they don\'92t see what God has shown you or they aren\'92t as open to God as you are.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf5 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Be quick\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls6\ilvl1
\f1\b0 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Too often we wait too long and miss the opportunity that God has for us.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Imagine if Joseph would have waited too long to leave Bethlehem.  Jesus may have died.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Some dreams have an expiration date, don\'92t let it expire!\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}James \'96 if you know the good you ought to do and don\'92t do it it is sin for you.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 \
\
\uc0\u8232 
\f0\b\fs36 WE\
\
\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\ls7\ilvl0
\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Need to bring people back to the message two weeks ago.\
{\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}Joseph was a normal guy like us but it was his heart toward God that was unique.\
}